<span class="s2">"SECONDARY-4855bf09-6765-48c4-a8f7-5dd189924589"</span><span class="w">
</span></code></pre><h3 id='settlement-debt-code-post-platformapi-settlement-secondary-market-code-description'>Description</h3>
<p>Records the settlement of a secondary market trade.</p>

<p>The response is a JSON string, containing a <code>repaymentBatchReference</code>, which will be included in several
webhooks that can help to track the arrival of the funds into the sellers account. These webhooks include:</p>

<ul>
<li><a href="/#webhooks-investment_repayment_instruction_received">INVESTMENT_REPAYMENT_INSTRUCTION_RECEIVED</a></li>
<li><a href="/#webhooks-investment_repayment_clearing">INVESTMENT_REPAYMENT_CLEARING</a></li>
<li><a href="/#webhooks-investment_repayment_batch_complete">INVESTMENT_REPAYMENT_BATCH_COMPLETE</a></li>
</ul>
